Q.2
 <!--Q 2. Write a HTML code which generates page with red background with a message
“warning” in large size .Add scrolling text “read the message” below it using embedding
stylesheet.-->

<html>
    <head>
        <style>
      body{
        background-color: red;
        
      }
      h1{
        margin-top: auto;
        text-align: center;
      }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>!!! This is the warning message !!!</h1>
        <marquee><p>read the messge !</p></marquee>
    </body>
</html>
